Package: quotai
Architecture: all
Depends: python3:any (>= 3.12),
         ${misc:Depends}
Description: Z.ai quota usage and reset-time CLI
 quotai queries the Z.ai quota endpoint and renders current usage, remaining
 capacity, and exact reset windows in readable terminal and machine-readable
 formats. It is useful when the upstream usage charts do not show enough detail
 about rolling quota resets.
